text: Harvest Moon, known in Japan as , is a farm simulation video game made by Pack-In-Video and published by Natsume in North America and Nintendo in PAL regions. It's about a farmer who has to make a great farm before the game reaches the end. He can also get married and have a baby. ==References== Category:1996 video games Category:Virtual Console games Category:Super Nintendo Entertainment System games
